      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "To discern the school's approach, you might look closely at the specific curriculum documents and learning objectives they provide. Determining \"educational necessity\" often requires seeing how these topics are integrated, such as whether they are being taught through social-emotional learning frameworks or as part of mandated state standards. Reviewing the school board's rationale or any public comments from their curriculum committee can also offer insight into their stated educational goals.",
      "source": "target",
